{"article_id":"tu1GGOdVMbAcd8Xq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The parents of American college student Otto Warmbier ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"who died after his detention in North Korea ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"on Friday countered President Trump ' s suggestion","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that Kim Jong Un was unaware of their son ' s treatment","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"- blaming the \" evil regime \" for Otto ' s death","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and saying","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"no amount of \" lavish praise \" can change that .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"The president drew bipartisan criticism","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"for saying during Thursday ' s summit in Hanoi","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that he takes Kim \" at his word . \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" I believe","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"something very bad happened to him , \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"leadership knew about it . \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Fred and Cindy Warmbier released a brief statement on Friday morning","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"reiterating their long-held claim","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that the regime is responsible for their son ' s death :","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" We have been respectful during this summit process .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Now we must speak out .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Kim and his evil regime are responsible for the death of our son Otto .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Kim and his evil regime are responsible for unimaginable cruelty and inhumanity .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"No excuses or lavish praise can change that . \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"White House Counselor Kellyanne Conway clarified in an interview Friday on Fox News , however ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that the president agrees with the family","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"and holds North Korea \" responsible. \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"She said","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Trump was only saying","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"there ' s no indication","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Kim knew","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"what happened at the time .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" Of course he holds North Korea responsible .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"He has deep affection","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"and shares the grief of the Warmbier family .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"That will never end , \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"The 22-year-old University of Virginia student died in June 2017","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"after being returned home in a vegetative state .","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"His parents have said","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"he was tortured .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"The suburban Cincinnati youth was visiting North Korea with a tour group","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"when he was detained in 2016","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"for allegedly stealing a propaganda poster .","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"North Korea has denied mistreating Warmbier .","depth":2},{"id":44,"text":"Trump ' s comments on the case drew criticism back home ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"recalling moments","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"like when he did not challenge Vladimir Putin 's denial of election meddling at their 2018 summit .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"`` We should n't be naive about this regime and about the way","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"they mistreat their own people .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"And certainly the way","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"they mistreated Otto Warmbier , ''","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Sen . Rob Portman , R-Ohio , said Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"There have been conflicting reports","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"over whether Warmbier was tortured .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"But Trump himself asserted in September 2017","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"that Warmbier was \" tortured beyond belief by North Korea . \"","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Last summer , Warmbier ' s parents praised Trump","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"after he said","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"the first summit with Kim might not have happened","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"if not for Warmbier ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"and that \" Otto did not die in vain . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":103,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":96,"right":102,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":75,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":67,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":62,"right":66,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":62,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":63,"right":65,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":4,"right":64,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":7,"right":73,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":68,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":69,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":82,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":77,"right":81,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":15,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":78,"right":80,"relation":"organization","nuc